cobalah ke Vichy.

511
00:43:33,384 --> 00:43:34,427
Siapa kau?

512
00:43:35,470 --> 00:43:37,388
Kukira aku hanya
sekadar seragam.

513
00:43:37,472 --> 00:43:39,432
Kau bukan cuma tentara Jerman.

514
00:43:40,600 --> 00:43:42,268
Apa kau putra seseorang?

