Undangan?

569
00:49:00,920 --> 00:49:02,338
Apa itu wanita muda yang
kau ceritakan, Fredrick?

570
00:49:02,421 --> 00:49:03,756
Ya, Dr. Goebbels.

571
00:49:04,090 --> 00:49:06,968
Emmanuelle, aku ingin
perkenalkan kau ke seseorang.

572
00:49:09,262 --> 00:49:13,391
Emmanuelle Mimieux,
inilah Menteri Propaganda,

573
00:49:14,058 --> 00:49:16,769
pemimpin seluruh
industri film Jerman

574
00:49:17,228 --> 00:49:21,065
dan karena aku kini aktor, dia
juga atasanku, Dr. Joseph Goebbels.

575
00:49:21,941 --> 00:49:24,318
Sudah kudengar
reputasimu, Nona Mimieux.

576
00:49:30,449 --> 00:49:33,744
Biasanya, inilah penerjemah
Prancis untuk Tuan Goebbels,

577
00:49:34,120 --> 00:49:35,663
Nona Francesca Mondino.

578
00:49:35,746 --> 00:49:36,789
Halo.

579
00:49:41,961 --> 00:49:42,962
Halo.

580
00:49:45,464 --> 00:49:47,383
Dan kau sudah jumpa si Mayor.

581
00:49:47,925 --> 00:49:51,512
Aku belum perkenalkan diriku,
Mayor Dieter Hellstrom dari Gestapo.

582
00:49:51,762 --> 00:49:53,264
Siap melayani, Nona.

583
00:49:53,973 --> 00:49:55,099
Biar aku...

584
00:49:56,309 --> 00:49:57,643
